{"tid":2176881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢炎?] 兒童醫院1歲半男童初步確診　與母均帶病毒抗體　料曾受感染","createTime":"2020-08-27T10:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T08:09:52.000Z","uid":78016,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e790e33c502ec5e5837dafbbfd2d9c119609ea22","tid":2176881,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200825/s00001/1598347599131/新冠肺炎-兒童醫院1歲半男童初步確診-與母均帶病毒抗體-料曾受感染\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200825%2Fs00001%2F1598347599131%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A21%E6%AD%B2%E5%8D%8A%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E8%88%87%E6%AF%8D%E5%9D%87%E5%B8%B6%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%8A%97%E9%AB%94-%E6%96%99%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%97%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=07b66b27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200825%2Fs00001%2F1598347599131%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A21%E6%AD%B2%E5%8D%8A%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E8%88%87%E6%AF%8D%E5%9D%87%E5%B8%B6%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%8A%97%E9%AB%94-%E6%96%99%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%97%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93&h=6ed7c120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200825/s00001/1598347599131/新冠肺炎-兒童醫院1歲半男童初步確診-與母均帶病毒抗體-料曾受感染</a><br />\n<br />\n何婉霞稱，該男童原定昨日入院進行已預約的小童疝氣手術，而兒童屬保護群組，為謹慎起見入院時為男童做檢測，結果發現其體內有抗體。他被送到兒童醫院的隔離病房，今日轉送伊利沙伯醫院檢查。醫管局與醫院感染控制組、衛生署商討後，相信男童沒有傳染風險，故未有病人及醫護人員被列為密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n又一單無啦啦感染左 無病徵 無啦啦好返 識行識走 驚乜?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b414cfb75c52edc60657ece468cec993375d2bd","tid":2176881,"uid":275238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:01:35.000Z","msg":"真係廢炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67506cf89344e5f927878193832dd4f584a99446","tid":2176881,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:26:30.000Z","msg":"唔知佢好番前有冇將病毒散播出去呢 <br />\n依對母子都幾好彩"},{"pid":"7c1fdfd3f78811c5773ceee98de474efe7d59c93","tid":2176881,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67506cf89344e5f927878193832dd4f584a99446","tid":2176881,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:26:30.000Z","msg":"唔知佢好番前有冇將病毒散播出去呢 <br />\n依對母子都幾好彩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"好多單都係咁<br />\n廢就廢啦 世紀疫症喎"},{"pid":"df48edb6da6ee3bf09df730d81dfa28a37a67b37","tid":2176881,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"後生又健康跟本容易好番，只不過後遺症就唔知點樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2609d23fa2dc72a55073273938e3c1638b109c6f","tid":2176881,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df48edb6da6ee3bf09df730d81dfa28a37a67b37","tid":2176881,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"後生又健康跟本容易好番，只不過後遺症就唔知點樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:13:58.000Z","msg":"識行識走 唔用藥會有咩後遺症"},{"pid":"5ae5ce807d85f12cad7f672e2d5a5e2dffb04b8c","tid":2176881,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">巴基爛坦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6122874b508c7c7da19f0c2b81464b616a1de64a","tid":2176881,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:19:38.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚： 咁先恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gi